frames.input.event

Class KeyShortcut

  • java.lang.Object
    • frames.input.Shortcut
      • frames.input.event.KeyShortcut

  • public class KeyShortcut
extends Shortcut
    This class represents KeyEvent shortcuts.

    Key shortcuts can be of one out of two forms: 1. Characters (e.g., 'a'); 2. Virtual keys (e.g., right arrow key); or, 2. Key combinations (e.g., CTRL key + virtual key representing 'a').
